<section>
	<h2>Purpose</h2>
	<p>This theme implements the requirements of the <a href="http://www.tbs-sct.gc.ca/pol/doc-eng.aspx?id=24227">Standard on Web Usability</a> and is recommended for use on all Government of Canada websites (except for Canada.ca).</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Use when</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>This theme must be used on Government of Canada websites (including web applications).</li>
	</ul>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Do not use when</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>This theme can only be used on Government of Canada websites.</li>
	</ul>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Working example</h2>
